WEBVTT

00:00:01.111 --> 00:00:03.643
U zimi 2012. godine

00:00:03.667 --> 00:00:05.684
posjetila sam kuću svoje bake

00:00:05.708 --> 00:00:07.351
u južnoj Indiji,

00:00:07.375 --> 00:00:08.684
mjestu gdje, usput,

00:00:08.708 --> 00:00:12.393
komarci imaju poseban tek
za krvlju Amerikanaca.

00:00:12.417 --> 00:00:13.518
(Smijeh)

00:00:13.542 --> 00:00:14.792
Nije šala.

00:00:15.375 --> 00:00:18.708
Dok sam bila ondje,
dobila sam neočekivan dar.

00:00:19.583 --> 00:00:22.101
Bio je to ovaj drevni instrument

00:00:22.125 --> 00:00:24.059
izrađen prije više od stoljeća,

00:00:24.083 --> 00:00:26.726
ručno izrezbaren iz rijetkog drveta,

00:00:26.750 --> 00:00:28.101
ispunjen biserima

00:00:28.125 --> 00:00:30.458
i s desecima metalnih žica.